00:30:35,760 --> 00:30:36,800
Did I not notice?

856
00:30:37,560 --> 00:30:38,880
Then why did I always choose you?

857
00:30:38,880 --> 00:30:40,040
Because to me,

858
00:30:40,040 --> 00:30:41,120
you're always number one.

859
00:30:41,680 --> 00:30:44,200
He is being so direct.

860
00:30:44,200 --> 00:30:46,040
You're always number one to me.

861
00:30:48,840 --> 00:30:49,720
Am I crazy

862
00:30:49,720 --> 00:30:51,280
to stay up late

863
00:30:51,280 --> 00:30:53,360
just for a chat?

864
00:30:53,360 --> 00:30:57,360
Yeah! Xiaowen is really straightforward.

865
00:30:59,960 --> 00:31:01,320
My thought has always been

866
00:31:01,320 --> 00:31:04,040
that I try to get to know you more.

867
00:31:06,480 --> 00:31:08,320
Youling asked me
why I kept asking you out.

868
00:31:08,320 --> 00:31:10,480
I think, first of all,

869
00:31:11,120 --> 00:31:12,200
when I'm with you,

870
00:31:13,080 --> 00:31:14,440
I don't have any

871
00:31:14,440 --> 00:31:15,840
feeling of tiredness.

872
00:31:15,840 --> 00:31:17,080
I feel no pressure.

873
00:31:17,080 --> 00:31:18,760
It makes me feel

874
00:31:18,760 --> 00:31:20,080
quite relaxed and happy.

875
00:31:20,800 --> 00:31:21,800
I think for me,

876
00:31:21,800 --> 00:31:22,560
that's the most important thing.

877
00:31:22,920 --> 00:31:24,440
Xuan immediately got the answer.

878
00:31:24,440 --> 00:31:25,440
She just wanted to hear that.

879
00:31:25,440 --> 00:31:26,280
Yes.

880
00:31:27,960 --> 00:31:29,640
Maybe you think

881
00:31:29,640 --> 00:31:30,320
you're only willing

882
00:31:31,000 --> 00:31:32,360
because

883
00:31:32,360 --> 00:31:33,320
you're not tired.

884
00:31:35,440 --> 00:31:36,720
You're starting to pre-judge me.

885
00:31:36,720 --> 00:31:37,880
I've already started pre-judging.

886
00:31:37,880 --> 00:31:38,640
I've already...

887
00:31:38,640 --> 00:31:40,080
I can't help it. I just...

888
00:31:40,800 --> 00:31:41,000
You...

889
00:31:41,440 --> 00:31:42,560
You're cracking me up.

890
00:31:43,680 --> 00:31:46,320
That's just my honest thought.

891
00:31:46,320 --> 00:31:47,560
First, I need to make sure

892
00:31:47,560 --> 00:31:48,520
that when I interact with her,

893
00:31:48,520 --> 00:31:49,760
I'm in a relaxed state.

894
00:31:49,760 --> 00:31:50,600
Then we can

895
00:31:50,600 --> 00:31:52,120
continue to get to know each other.

896
00:31:53,120 --> 00:31:54,120
If we can't even do that,

897
00:31:54,120 --> 00:31:56,120
what else is there to talk about?

898
00:31:56,120 --> 00:31:56,360
Right?

899
00:31:56,360 --> 00:31:56,880
So that's why

900
00:31:56,880 --> 00:31:58,840
I don't bother getting to know others.

901
00:31:58,840 --> 00:32:00,640
I think there's no need.

902
00:32:02,320 --> 00:32:03,040
So tell me,

903
00:32:03,040 --> 00:32:04,920
what do you think I'm like?

904
00:32:05,320 --> 00:32:06,240
He managed to cheer her up.

905
00:32:06,240 --> 00:32:07,160
Alright, she is cheered up now.

906
00:32:07,160 --> 00:32:09,800
This kind of question clearly shows
she is feeling good now.

907
00:32:10,800 --> 00:32:12,160
You start saying something
and stop halfway.

908
00:32:12,160 --> 00:32:13,320
It drives people crazy.

909
00:32:14,960 --> 00:32:15,880
You're talking about me?

910
00:32:16,760 --> 00:32:18,360
I say half and stop?

911
00:32:19,080 --> 00:32:20,120
I think I'm very direct.

912
00:32:22,560 --> 00:32:23,160
Really?

913
00:32:23,160 --> 00:32:25,000
Can I throw something at you?

914
00:32:26,240 --> 00:32:28,960
Is that your feeling about me?

915
00:32:28,960 --> 00:32:29,200
Yes.

916
00:32:29,200 --> 00:32:30,600
I say half and stop?

917
00:32:30,600 --> 00:32:30,920
Yes.

918
00:32:30,920 --> 00:32:32,600
What have I said half and stopped?

919
00:32:33,240 --> 00:32:34,120
You did it too much.

920
00:32:35,040 --> 00:32:36,120
Give me an example.

921
00:32:37,200 --> 00:32:38,200
Give me an example.

922
00:32:38,200 --> 00:32:39,200
I can't give an example.

923
00:32:39,200 --> 00:32:40,280
Can't give an example?

924
00:32:41,000 --> 00:32:42,240
It's just because there were too many.

925
00:32:42,240 --> 00:32:43,480
I can't think of one.

926
00:32:44,320 --> 00:32:45,680
I can't give an example. It's too hard.

927
00:32:45,680 --> 00:32:46,960
I think I'm quite direct.

928
00:32:50,080 --> 00:32:51,120
So funny.

929
00:32:53,040 --> 00:32:54,760
So you still don't understand me.

930
00:32:55,240 --> 00:32:55,600
Right?

931
00:32:55,920 --> 00:32:57,160
But doesn't he want to understand?

932
00:32:57,880 --> 00:32:59,520
I don't think you understand me either.

933
00:32:59,520 --> 00:33:01,840
I think the impression
you have of me is also

934
00:33:02,400 --> 00:33:03,560
not so accurate.

935
00:33:04,960 --> 00:33:05,560
So

936
00:33:05,560 --> 00:33:07,000
what we're doing

937
00:33:07,000 --> 00:33:08,440
is getting to know each other.

938
00:33:08,720 --> 00:33:09,400
(- Yes.
- Yes.)

939
00:33:09,400 --> 00:33:10,640
(Well said.)

940
00:33:11,640 --> 00:33:13,080
Who could possibly...

941
00:33:13,080 --> 00:33:14,880
We're only thirty.

942
00:33:14,880 --> 00:33:16,000
You're not thirty yet.

943
00:33:17,360 --> 00:33:18,920
You...

944
00:33:18,920 --> 00:33:20,000
Look at you.

945
00:33:20,000 --> 00:33:21,240
So old-fashioned.

946
00:33:21,240 --> 00:33:22,920
Always obsessing over age.

947
00:33:22,920 --> 00:33:23,720
What's your problem?

948
00:33:23,720 --> 00:33:25,640
I'm "old-fashioned"?

949
00:33:26,280 --> 00:33:27,840
Talk properly.

950
00:33:27,840 --> 00:33:28,800
Granny thinking.

951
00:33:31,080 --> 00:33:32,480
Are you asking for trouble?

952
00:33:32,480 --> 00:33:33,720
Obsessing over age.

953
00:33:35,360 --> 00:33:36,440
They're a perfect match.

954
00:33:36,880 --> 00:33:38,920
Only Xiaowen can deal with Xuan.

955
00:33:38,920 --> 00:33:39,760
Yeah.

956
00:33:39,760 --> 00:33:40,200
You know.

957
00:33:40,200 --> 00:33:41,880
It has to be his way.

958
00:33:41,880 --> 00:33:42,960
If she said it to someone else,

959
00:33:42,960 --> 00:33:44,720
they may feel a bit offended.

960
00:33:44,720 --> 00:33:45,960
But he said, "old-fashioned."

961
00:33:45,960 --> 00:33:46,800
See what happened?

962
00:33:48,960 --> 00:33:49,920
(At the beginning,)

963
00:33:49,920 --> 00:33:52,600
the conversation was meaningless.

964
00:33:52,600 --> 00:33:53,680
Unproductive.

965
00:33:54,720 --> 00:33:56,440
I felt she was rejecting me.

966
00:33:57,200 --> 00:33:58,520
But she slowly

967
00:33:58,520 --> 00:34:00,520
let go of that attitude.

968
00:34:01,280 --> 00:34:01,760
Okay.

969
00:34:01,760 --> 00:34:04,640
Then we truly talked about

970
00:34:04,640 --> 00:34:06,000
our feelings.

971
00:34:07,920 --> 00:34:08,480
(At that time,)

972
00:34:08,480 --> 00:34:10,160
(I shut myself off.)

973
00:34:10,800 --> 00:34:11,960
(But I could feel)

974
00:34:11,960 --> 00:34:14,480
(that he wasn't affected by my mood.)

975
00:34:14,480 --> 00:34:16,400
(He was earnestly expressing himself.)

976
00:34:16,400 --> 00:34:18,680
Yeah, she's also very self-aware.

977
00:34:18,680 --> 00:34:20,680
(And then I started to realize)

978
00:34:20,680 --> 00:34:21,320
(something was off.)

979
00:34:21,320 --> 00:34:22,120
(I realized)

980
00:34:23,480 --> 00:34:25,160
it was because I started to care.

981
00:34:25,920 --> 00:34:27,400
I started to take it seriously.

982
00:34:27,400 --> 00:34:29,400
That's why I became like this.

983
00:34:29,920 --> 00:34:31,280
If I weren't interested

984
00:34:31,280 --> 00:34:31,880
in him,

985
00:34:31,880 --> 00:34:32,640
if I didn't care,

986
00:34:32,640 --> 00:34:34,480
why would I mind

987
00:34:35,360 --> 00:34:37,120
if someone else asked him out,

988
00:34:37,120 --> 00:34:39,480
or if he exchanged a word
with someone else?

989
00:34:39,480 --> 00:34:41,400
Why would I

990
00:34:41,400 --> 00:34:43,080
observe all that?

991
00:34:43,960 --> 00:34:44,920
Jealous?

992
00:34:44,920 --> 00:34:46,320
Are you jealous?

993
00:34:48,160 --> 00:34:49,560
You're such a child.

994
00:34:49,560 --> 00:34:50,920
(And she's calling him a child.)

995
00:34:50,920 --> 00:34:52,720
Is there anything wrong with that?

996
00:34:52,720 --> 00:34:54,040
It's good.

997
00:34:54,040 --> 00:34:54,560
Child.

998
00:34:55,320 --> 00:34:55,920
Call me "sister".

999
00:34:56,880 --> 00:34:58,880
- "Sister"?
- "Sister"?

1000
00:35:00,080 --> 00:35:00,480
What?

1001
00:35:00,480 --> 00:35:02,600
What kind of weird habit is that?

1002
00:35:03,680 --> 00:35:04,840
Weird habit?

1003
00:35:05,960 --> 00:35:07,600
But I am older than you, aren't I?

1004
00:35:09,800 --> 00:35:11,320
I really think

1005
00:35:11,760 --> 00:35:13,480
being childish is wonderful.

1006
00:35:13,640 --> 00:35:14,320
Yeah.

1007
00:35:14,320 --> 00:35:16,560
In a relationship,
you can be spoiled like a child.

1008
00:35:16,800 --> 00:35:18,440
You're avoiding it.

1009
00:35:19,680 --> 00:35:20,120
So funny.

1010
00:35:20,120 --> 00:35:20,640
What?

1011
00:35:21,080 --> 00:35:21,560
Nothing.

1012
00:35:22,440 --> 00:35:23,840
Looks like she got over it.

1013
00:35:23,840 --> 00:35:24,720
Happy now.

1014
00:35:25,280 --> 00:35:27,000
(I think after we talked,)

1015
00:35:27,480 --> 00:35:28,480
(we understood)

1016
00:35:28,480 --> 00:35:29,760
(each other)

1017
00:35:29,760 --> 00:35:30,720
(better.)

1018
00:35:31,160 --> 00:35:32,440
(It would make our interactions)

1019
00:35:32,440 --> 00:35:33,720
(more natural.)

1020
00:35:38,520 --> 00:35:39,920
Why sign after
having a conversation with me?

1021
00:35:43,400 --> 00:35:44,720
I wonder what's for tomorrow.

1022
00:35:45,480 --> 00:35:46,000
Good night.

1023
00:35:46,560 --> 00:35:47,040
Good night.

1024
00:35:47,440 --> 00:35:47,800
Bye.

1025
00:35:53,200 --> 00:35:54,160
Watching this part,

1026
00:35:54,160 --> 00:35:55,840
my mood went up and down.

1027
00:35:55,840 --> 00:35:56,720
Yeah.

1028
00:35:56,720 --> 00:35:59,000
We watched the dates of several couples.

1029
00:35:59,000 --> 00:36:01,480
Which scene left the deepest impression?

1030
00:36:01,480 --> 00:36:03,120
The guy was taking photos
of the scenery.

1031
00:36:03,120 --> 00:36:04,480
(Evonne Sie)
The girl was taking photos of the guy.

1032
00:36:04,480 --> 00:36:06,000
What's in the picture
reflects what's on their minds.

1033
00:36:06,760 --> 00:36:07,760
That part

1034
00:36:07,760 --> 00:36:10,080
was quite pleasant.

1035
00:36:10,080 --> 00:36:11,320
I really like

1036
00:36:11,320 --> 00:36:13,360
Danqi's state in that part.

1037
00:36:13,360 --> 00:36:14,240
Me too.

1038
00:36:14,240 --> 00:36:14,640
Yeah.

1039
00:36:14,640 --> 00:36:15,680
She was expressing

1040
00:36:15,680 --> 00:36:16,920
her affection for that person

1041
00:36:16,920 --> 00:36:18,000
with restraint.

1042
00:36:18,000 --> 00:36:19,080
That kind of devotion

1043
00:36:19,080 --> 00:36:20,240
would move anyone.

1044
00:36:20,240 --> 00:36:21,000
Yeah.

1045
00:36:21,000 --> 00:36:21,840
And I think Danqi

1046
00:36:21,840 --> 00:36:22,840
has one great quality.

1047
00:36:22,840 --> 00:36:24,680
She could actually sense

1048
00:36:24,680 --> 00:36:25,840
that Zhou Youling

1049
00:36:25,840 --> 00:36:26,960
wasn't focused on her.

1050
00:36:26,960 --> 00:36:28,280
She was aware of

1051
00:36:28,280 --> 00:36:29,000
what was going on.

1052
00:36:29,000 --> 00:36:30,320
But she didn't press him.

1053
00:36:30,320 --> 00:36:31,840
Nor did she amplify that.

1054
00:36:31,840 --> 00:36:32,960
I'll just sing for you

1055
00:36:32,960 --> 00:36:33,840
to make you happy.

1056
00:36:35,000 --> 00:36:36,520
She wanted to cheer him up.

1057
00:36:36,520 --> 00:36:39,440
(Zhang Chunye)That was more important
than getting an answer.

1058
00:36:39,440 --> 00:36:40,640
That's really charming.

1059
00:36:40,640 --> 00:36:41,920
I find that very touching.

1060
00:36:41,920 --> 00:36:42,760
Yeah.

1061
00:36:42,760 --> 00:36:44,120
This is actually

1062
00:36:44,120 --> 00:36:46,720
the shift in women's approach to love.

1063
00:36:46,720 --> 00:36:47,760
We used to say

1064
00:36:47,760 --> 00:36:49,520
that women were bound by love.

1065
00:36:49,520 --> 00:36:50,120
That's because

1066
00:36:50,120 --> 00:36:51,360
we wanted to be loved.

1067
00:36:52,160 --> 00:36:53,200
But I think Danqi

1068
00:36:53,200 --> 00:36:54,960
has moved to the mode of loving.

1069
00:36:54,960 --> 00:36:56,720
Loving you makes me happy.

1070
00:36:56,720 --> 00:36:57,920
I'm in control.

1071
00:36:57,920 --> 00:36:59,480
This is the attitude towards love

1072
00:36:59,480 --> 00:37:00,640
of a modern woman.

1073
00:37:00,640 --> 00:37:02,240
(Gained a lot)
I've learned so much from her.

1074
00:37:02,240 --> 00:37:02,920
I think.

1075
00:37:02,920 --> 00:37:03,720
Yeah.

1076
00:37:03,720 --> 00:37:06,080
Among all the dating details,

1077
00:37:06,080 --> 00:37:07,920
what struck you the most?

1078
00:37:07,920 --> 00:37:09,760
Wentao and Hui

1079
00:37:09,760 --> 00:37:10,640
got along well.

1080
00:37:10,640 --> 00:37:11,920
But after he came back,

1081
00:37:11,920 --> 00:37:13,440
he went to chat with Xuan.

1082
00:37:13,440 --> 00:37:14,760
Xuan turned him down.

1083
00:37:14,760 --> 00:37:17,080
That surprised me quite a bit.

1084
00:37:17,080 --> 00:37:18,080
I think she might be

1085
00:37:18,080 --> 00:37:19,240
a bit overly defensive.

1086
00:37:19,240 --> 00:37:20,680
It's understandable.

1087
00:37:20,680 --> 00:37:22,480
More or less,

1088
00:37:22,480 --> 00:37:23,920
we've felt that way

1089
00:37:23,920 --> 00:37:25,280
in real life.

1090
00:37:25,280 --> 00:37:26,920
Definitely.

1091
00:37:26,920 --> 00:37:27,800
It's like,

1092
00:37:27,800 --> 00:37:29,320
you're so popular,

1093
00:37:29,320 --> 00:37:31,600
and you haven't given me a clear sign.

1094
00:37:31,600 --> 00:37:33,520
We've read too many novels.

1095
00:37:33,520 --> 00:37:34,520
She wanted him

1096
00:37:34,520 --> 00:37:35,600
to rush to her

1097
00:37:35,600 --> 00:37:36,560
when she turned around.

1098
00:37:37,080 --> 00:37:37,440
What's wrong?

1099
00:37:37,440 --> 00:37:38,280
What are you thinking?"

1100
00:37:38,600 --> 00:37:39,840
Let me explain.

1101
00:37:39,840 --> 00:37:40,280
Sister.

1102
00:37:41,440 --> 00:37:42,360
You called me "sister"?

1103
00:37:43,200 --> 00:37:44,440
You're so childish.

1104
00:37:44,440 --> 00:37:45,720
Do you know me?

1105
00:37:46,640 --> 00:37:48,320
I think being childish is wonderful.

1106
00:37:48,320 --> 00:37:49,960
Being childish is wonderful.

1107
00:37:52,280 --> 00:37:53,000
But if he

1108
00:37:53,000 --> 00:37:53,720
rushes to you

1109
00:37:53,720 --> 00:37:54,400
(Xia Zhiguang)
like in novels,

1110
00:37:54,400 --> 00:37:55,880
regardless of anything,

1111
00:37:56,320 --> 00:37:57,560
it's disrespectful to others.

1112
00:37:57,560 --> 00:37:59,240
So that's just novels.

1113
00:37:59,240 --> 00:38:01,480
It doesn't happen in real life.

1114
00:38:01,480 --> 00:38:02,240
You can't live

1115
00:38:02,240 --> 00:38:03,760
with a guy like that.

1116
00:38:03,760 --> 00:38:05,400
Actually,

1117
00:38:05,400 --> 00:38:06,960
politely accepting

1118
00:38:06,960 --> 00:38:08,000
the invitation

1119
00:38:08,000 --> 00:38:09,320
was the decent thing to do.

1120
00:38:09,320 --> 00:38:11,080
No matter what happens,

1121
00:38:11,080 --> 00:38:12,120
give them a chance

1122
00:38:12,120 --> 00:38:13,440
if you care about them.

1123
00:38:13,440 --> 00:38:15,160
So does the "sister" trick work?

1124
00:38:15,160 --> 00:38:16,560
(Zhang Zining)
It works very well.

1125
00:38:16,560 --> 00:38:16,800
Yeah?

1126
00:38:16,800 --> 00:38:17,680
Because

1127
00:38:17,680 --> 00:38:18,920
it's a playful coquetry

1128
00:38:18,920 --> 00:38:20,000
in a relationship.

1129
00:38:20,600 --> 00:38:22,080
Why "sister"?

1130
00:38:22,720 --> 00:38:24,240
There's a context.

1131
00:38:24,240 --> 00:38:25,520
The girl said,

1132
00:38:25,520 --> 00:38:26,360
"Call me sister."

1133
00:38:26,360 --> 00:38:27,040
(Really?)
Sister.

1134
00:38:28,640 --> 00:38:30,080
Does this really work, sister?

1135
00:38:31,720 --> 00:38:32,800
Sister.

1136
00:38:32,800 --> 00:38:34,840
Sister, just give me a heads-up.

1137
00:38:34,840 --> 00:38:35,560
(Cracking up)
It works?

1138
00:38:35,560 --> 00:38:35,960
No.

1139
00:38:35,960 --> 00:38:36,760
No, Guangzhi.

1140
00:38:36,760 --> 00:38:37,840
You're missing something.

1141
00:38:37,840 --> 00:38:40,160
(Acting cute)
